      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What are CSS Icons?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "CSS icons are visual symbols used in UI. They can be added using icon fonts, SVG, or image-based methods."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using Font Awesome"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<i class=\"fas fa-home\"></i>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using Material Icons"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons\" rel=\"stylesheet\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<span class=\"material-icons\">favorite</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using SVG Icons"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\">\n  <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" fill=\"blue\" />\n</svg>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Styling Icons with CSS"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "css",
      "value": "i {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  color: red;\n}\n\n.material-icons {\n  font-size: 30px;\n  color: green;\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Icon Sizes"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
